OL,3,CTreasury minister fails to rule out
OL,4,Ctaxing high-value homeowners in Budget
OL,6,FA treasury minister has failed to rule
OL,7,Fout taxing high-value homeowners in
OL,8,Fthe Budget, after reports the
OL,9,FChancellor is considering hitting the
OL,10,Fmost expensive properties with capital
OL,11,Fgains tax.
OL,13,FThe Times reported that Rachel Reeves
OL,14,Fcould end the current exemption from
OL,15,Fcapital gains tax (CGT) for primary
OL,16,Fresidences, as she tries to find ways
OL,17,Fto raise cash in the autumn Budget.
