OL,6,FThe government rarely comments
OL,7,Fpublicly on speculation ahead of the
OL,8,Fbudget, but they do often privately
OL,9,Fbrief potential plans to the media to
OL,10,Fsee how they might be received.
OL,12,FThe Times report is one of a string of
OL,13,Fpotential tax changes appearing in
OL,14,Fnewspapers in recent weeks, including
OL,15,Freports the Treasury could scrap stamp
OL,16,Fduty and replace it with a national
OL,17,Fproperty tax.
