OL,6,FEnding the exemption from CGT for main
OL,7,Fhomes would see higher-rate taxpayers
OL,8,Fpay 24% of any gain in the value of
OL,9,Ftheir home, while basic rate taxpayers
OL,10,Fwould be hit with an 18% levy.
