OL,6,FThe threshold is still under
OL,7,Fconsideration but a #1.5 million
OL,8,Fstarting point would hit around
OL,9,F120,000 homeowners who are higher-rate
OL,10,Ftaxpayers with capital gains tax bills
OL,11,Fof #199,973, the newspaper reported.
OL,13,FEnding primary residence relief could
OL,14,Fdeter people from selling their homes,
OL,15,Fslowing the housing market and could
OL,16,Fhave a particular impact for older
OL,17,Fpeople looking to downsize.
