OL,6,FThe Guardian also reported on Monday
OL,7,Fthat the Treasury is considering plans
OL,8,Fto raise money from a tax on the sale
OL,9,Fof homes worth more than #500,000 as
OL,10,Fpart of an overhaul of stamp duty on
OL,11,Fowner-occupied homes.
OL,13,FNo final decision has been made, but
OL,14,Fit is thought this national tax could
OL,15,Fhelp build a model for local levies to
OL,16,Freplace council tax in the medium term.
OL,18,FBuyers pay stamp duty under the
OL,19,Fexisting framework, if they purchase
OL,20,Fproperty worth more than #125,000.
