OL,6,FThe new levy would be paid by owner-
OL,7,Foccupiers on houses worth more than
OL,8,F#500,000 when they sell their home,
OL,9,Fwith the amount due determined by the
OL,10,Fvalue of the property and a rate set
OL,11,Fby the government.
OL,13,FThe Labour government has ruled out
OL,14,Fincreasing income tax, employees'
OL,15,Fnational insurance contributions and
OL,16,FVAT, restricting Reeves' options when
OL,17,Fit comes to raising money.
